node.text:
The perfect gentlemen’s folding knife doesn’t exiss…. @woox.outdoor I stand corrected.
Options:
-	Walnut 
-	Carbon+ walnut

PRODUCT DESCRIPTION

From traditional techniques to cutting-edge technologies, with Leggenda we have pushed the boundaries of what is possible. Years in the making, Leggenda is a one-of-a-kind folding knife which blends Carbon Fiber, steel and Real American Walnut for the first time ever. Leggenda distills the world-class performance of our knife makers into a modern, high performing, and outstanding EDC knife. Leggenda features: High carbon steel D2 Mil specs finished.  This steel is known to be one of the longer-lasting edge retention steel. D2 steel is an air-hardening, high carbon, high chromium tool steel with extremely high wear resisting properties.  
-	IKBS thrust bearing pivot system. It delivers fast flipper deployment and smooth operation.
-	Cutting-edge Walnut with Carbon fiber handle. . The scales have been machined out to accept steel liners that give the knife strength while reducing the overall weight.
-	Sturdy with a reliable liner lock blade locking system 
-	Reversible stainless-steel clip and screws

Merging innovation and tradition: Leggenda is a symbol of excellence, performance and design. 
#foldingblade #knife #blade #woox #blacksmith #outdoors #bfg #whatareyoubuildingfor
